soil my daughter's body.

286
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,040
Xuanli,

287
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,440
how are you...

288
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:11,080
At your age,

289
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:14,060
you should be married and have children,

290
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:18,880
living a life like other women.

291
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:22,880
Blame me for being too cowardly back then,

292
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:27,000
making you end up like this.

293
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:35,440
Live well after you get out.

294
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:43,800
Here they come.

295
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:46,320
Freshly baked hot sesame cakes.

296
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,240
Here, smell how good they are.

297
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,760
What a fragrant sesame cake.

298
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:50,680
Here,

299
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,920
you and the young lady share one. This is too big for me.

300
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,880
Jueming, let's share one.

301
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:00,920
Have you ever encountered such a bizarre case before?

302
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,600
When I was young,

303
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:06,440
it was a spectacular scene with flags fluttering and drums beating.

304
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,680
I followed Chief Catcher Qin,

305
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:10,210
and there was no magical case we didn't solve.

306
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:12,920
Then in your opinion,

307
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,840
between Zhao Xuanli and her mother,

308
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,080
who is the real culprit?

309
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,320
You lack vision.

310
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,640
You always ask such specific questions.

311
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,840
Let me tell you first.

312
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:24,520
I found this shaman to be truly miraculous.

313
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:28,740
What do we care about most in our line of work?

314
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,760
Coming and going safely, right?

315
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:32,240
So that day,

316
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:35,880
I wore plain clothes to the temple to pray

317
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,720
and ask for a peace amulet for everyone.

318
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:40,080
Right after I finished praying and stepped out of the temple,

319
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,720
I saw that shaman standing there.

320
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:43,680
Our eyes met.

321
00:21:43,760 --> 00:21:46,200
I suddenly felt a special connection.

322
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:47,680
I walked over,

323
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:50,000
and she immediately told me what I prayed for

324
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,560
and what I asked for today.

325
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:52,400
That amazing?

326
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,160
Let me tell you,

327
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,240
when I went out to pray that day,

328
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,880
I didn't even tell your mother.

329
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:58,160
How do you think she knew what I was going to pray for?

330
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:58,920
Right?

331
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,840
So,

332
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,560
this shaman

333
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,320
is really magical.

334
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,240
Chief Catcher Su,

335
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:08,560
Actually, for this shaman to know what you prayed for

336
00:22:08,560 --> 00:22:09,800
is very simple.

337
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:12,520
Because she has many followers

338
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,940
who pretend to be commoners and blend in.

339
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:17,680
Then when you kneel on the cushion and pray,

340
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,200
they will listen closely

341
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:20,800
to what you are praying for.

342
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:21,880
When you come out,

343
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,920
the followers will tell the shaman.

344
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:26,360
Then the shaman met you.

345
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:29,000
Judging by your outfit,

346
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,400
you must be a master.

347
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:34,210
I have been waiting for you for a long time.

348
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:36,520
Waiting for me?

349
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:37,680
If it were someone like me,

350
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,240
I wouldn't say my prayers out loud.

351
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,400
I'd just recite them silently in my heart.

352
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,160
How would she know?

353
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:41,840
Right.

354
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,400
That's also very simple.

355
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:45,720
There are so many pilgrims going to the temple every day.

356
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,080
She just needs to catch one or two

357
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:48,120
to make a fortune.

358
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,320
Oh no.

359
00:22:51,080 --> 00:22:51,840
I'm doomed.

360
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,600
I bought so many of these peace amulets from her.

361
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:56,240
You each have one, right?

362
00:22:56,280 --> 00:22:57,280
I gave them all to you.

363
00:22:57,280 --> 00:22:58,680
I have one for myself too.

364
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:00,560
I've been fooled.

365
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:02,760
She completely scammed me out of my money.

366
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:03,560
Constable Su,

367
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:05,440
peace amulets are for peace.

368
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:07,640
It doesn't matter who sold them to you.

369
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,280
What matters is our intention.

370
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:10,040
Right.

371
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:11,960
So according to what you said,

372
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:14,640
you don't believe the shaman has the ability to foresee the future.

373
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:17,160
You don't believe she can kill with curses either.

374
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,040
She can't.

375
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:20,480
Neither can Zhao Xuanli.

376
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,080
That's not right.

377
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:25,880
When Zhao Xuanli cast the curse that day,

378
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,600
you were clearly in pain.

379
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,460
Does it still hurt?

380
00:23:33,040 --> 00:23:34,040
I was pretending.

381
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,600
I just wanted to test her

382
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:41,640
to see if she really believed her curse could kill.

383
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,160
If she was lying herself,

384
00:23:45,280 --> 00:23:46,240
when I felt sick,

385
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:48,680
she would have shown a hint of surprise.

386
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:51,120
But her expression was calm at the time.

387
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:53,970
This shows she really believes she knows curses,

388
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,480
rather than lying.

389
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,240
You brat, you're quite sly.

390
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:01,700
I don't believe that in this world

391
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,170
curses can kill people.

392
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:05,520
But what if they do exist?

393
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:07,200
Isn't it too dangerous for you to do this?

394
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,600
Then I wouldn't die either.

395
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:09,640
She said it herself.

396
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:12,160
The curse requires a name and hair to match.

397
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:13,320
It has your hair,

398
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:15,290
and the name Jueming written on it.

399
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,600
Since you are so certain

400
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:22,200
that Zhao Xuanli is not the real killer,

401
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,840
why did you take her to the government office?

402
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:26,120
To show the suspect, of course.

403
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:28,440
Fan Le took Zhao Xuanli's money,

404
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:30,280
so he must have hidden it at home.

405
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:32,280
But when the four of us went to his house that day,

406
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:33,880
there was no money in the house.

407
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,120
This shows one thing:

408
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:38,240
someone must have arrived at the crime scene before us.

409
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,530
We need to find this person.

410
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:46,000
So Zhao Xuanli's mother was just taking the fall for her,

411
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:48,080
and she isn't the real killer either.

412
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:50,940
Then the real killer must be related to Zhao Xuanli.

413
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:53,400
Let's go right now

414
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,920
and investigate all the social connections

415
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,320
of Zhao Xuanli's family.

416
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:58,920
Wait for me to finish this bowl of porridge!

417
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,680
Solving the case is more important. Let's go.

418
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:01,680
Then take a pancake.

419
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,340
Here, take a pancake with you.

420
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:05,840
I'll go buy you a hot one,

421
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:07,040
fresh out of the oven.

422
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,600
Safety comes first,

423
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:10,160
and cases can wait.

424
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:11,760
You always forget that.

425
00:25:12,320 --> 00:25:14,520
The porridge is cold. I'll go heat it up.

426
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,480
No,

427
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:22,840
why do I feel like Zhao Xuanli is the killer?

428
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:26,280
Her mother is a sorceress,

429
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,760
just a fraud.

430
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,240
Her father is a gambler.

431
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:32,240
How good can a child raised by them be?

432
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,240
The law is based on facts.

433
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:38,520
We can't just rely on subjective assumptions.

434
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,180
How about this?

435
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,320
Let's think again.

436
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:47,800
What do these crime scenes have in common?

437
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,800
The victims' pupils

438
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:52,160
were all dilated.

439
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:55,800
There was a fallen bucket next to Niu Dali's body,

440
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:58,800
and there was a fallen kettle next to Fan Le's body.

441
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:05,480
This shows they experienced extreme thirst before they died.

442
00:26:06,360 --> 00:26:07,560
With these symptoms,

443
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:12,140
it's highly likely they were poisoned by datura before they died.

444
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:14,360
The suspect poisoned them.

445
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:16,240
Once poisoned by datura,

446
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,720
one will experience blurred vision,

447
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:18,640
extreme thirst,

448
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,480
a rapid heartbeat,

449
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:21,120
and hallucinations.

450
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:24,770
They most likely chose to commit suicide while hallucinating.

451
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:26,640
I got it.

452
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,040
What are you doing? Where are you going?

453
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:28,800
To test the poison.

454
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,260
How do you test the poison?

455
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:31,000
Hey.

456
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,800
This is the datura flower.

457
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:39,440
What are you doing?

458
00:26:39,440 --> 00:26:42,280
Taking a small amount simulates the poisoning.

459
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,560
After I pass out later,

460
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:48,400
remember to pour licorice and mung bean soup into my mouth.

461
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,400
Aren't these mung beans?

462
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,480
Isn't that a stove?

463
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,320
Mother.

464
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:17,200
What's wrong?

465
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:17,920
Mother.

466
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:20,960
Are you all right, Jueming?

467
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:23,960
Mother,

468
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:26,000
I missed you so much.

469
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,360
Don't be afraid.

470
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:33,160
It's all right.

471
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:53,800
As you two know,

472
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:56,240
the men who come here are either looking for pleasure

473
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:57,600
or entertainment.

474
00:27:57,640 --> 00:28:00,440
They might be intimately involved with the courtesans,

475
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:01,840
even acting desperately in love.

476
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:03,920
But to have them commit murder for anyone?

477
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,840
That is absolutely impossible.

478
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:09,250
Does she have any special regular customers?

479
00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:10,480
There is one.

480
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:12,680
He always asks for Zhao Xuanli.

481
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:15,560
He also came to ask me about redeeming her

482
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:17,400
and how much money it would take.

483
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,760
I just gave a random number,

484
00:28:18,760 --> 00:28:19,890
and he noted it down.

485
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:21,400
What is his name?

486
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,920
Jixiang,

487
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:25,050
a laborer at Jinxiu Silk Workshop.

488
00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:26,960
He came today.

489
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:29,880
I told him Zhao Xuanli went out early in the morning.

490
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:32,240
So he left this wooden box with me

491
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:35,080
and said to give it to Zhao Xuanli when she returns.

492
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,520
A wooden box.

493
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:56,720
You're awake.

494
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,420
You're finally awake.

495
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,120
You scared me to death.

496
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:02,920
Look at how many bowls of mung bean soup I've fed you.

497
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,640
And you also had so much licorice.

498
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,900
I was really afraid you wouldn't wake up.

499
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,440
Thank you.

500
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,400
You scared me.

501
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:13,280
Do you want some more?

502
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:19,920
Are you okay?

503
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,100
Are you still hallucinating?

504
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:33,600
Did I say any nonsense

505
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:35,020
or do anything stupid?

506
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,280
No.

507
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:50,160
By the way,

508
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,600
The effect of this Datura flower

509
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:54,920
can temporarily incapacitate a person.

510
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,420
So it's impossible for him

511
00:29:58,360 --> 00:30:00,200
to commit suicide.

512
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:02,720
I see.

513
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,760
Why didn't I think of that?

514
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:22,840
Did Zhao Xuanli's father die at home?

515
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:26,880
Where are you going?

516
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,640
You haven't fully recovered yet.

517
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,700
Hurry up. The lord is looking for you.

518
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:31,480
Hurry up.

519
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:32,960
What's the matter, officers?

520
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:35,280
Tell the lord what you saw.

521
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,240
Speak.

522
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,360
A man was knocking on the door just now.

523
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:40,520
He left when he saw no one inside.

524
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,820
What does he look like?

525
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,810
About this tall,

526
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:44,880
and thin.

527
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,340
With somewhat small eyes.

528
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:53,320
I was just about to look for you two.

529
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,800
I found a suspect here.

530
00:30:54,840 --> 00:30:56,120
His name is Jixiang.

531
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:58,560
He went to Yichun Brothel to look for Zhao Xuanli.

532
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,080
And he even asked the madam

533
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:02,680
how much it would cost to redeem Zhao Xuanli.

534
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,600
Jixiang?

535
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:04,360
Yeah.

536
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:06,000
He came looking for Zhao Xuanli today.

537
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,600
Found she wasn't in the room.

538
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:08,680
Xiao Li, come here.

539
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,320
Coming.

540
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:15,440
Not only that.

541
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:18,440
Back then, when Niu Dali assaulted Zhao Xuanli,

542
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,140
he was the one who reported it.

543
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:24,260
We found out Jixiang works at Jinxiu Silk Workshop.

544
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:25,980
So we went to the workshop.

545
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,280
When I saw him,

546
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:30,360
I realized he was the one who reported the case three years ago.

547
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,200
Let's go to Xiao Li's house for a few drinks after this.

548
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,160
Okay.

549
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,160
Officers.

550
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:35,320
Officers.

551
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,680
Someone is raping a young girl.

552
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,800
Someone is raping a young girl.

553
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:38,920
Where? Over there.

554
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,720
At that time,

555
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:41,560
he said he was on his way home,

556
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,280
saw Niu Dali's beastly act,

557
00:31:43,320 --> 00:31:44,640
and hurried to report it.

558
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,520
But just now,

559
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:48,160
when he learned that Zhao Xuanli and her mother both turned themselves in,

560
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:49,400
he seemed very surprised.

561
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:50,560
How is that possible?

562
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:51,760
Killing with curses?

563
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,160
Officers, you actually believe that?

564
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,160
Of course we do.

565
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:55,480
She confessed,

566
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:58,880
and explained the details of the crime very thoroughly.

567
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:02,600
I suspect this Jixiang developed feelings for Zhao Xuanli.

568
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,780
He just committed the murder for her.

569
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:09,240
So I used talk about believing in curses to trick him.

570
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,240
Alright, you don't need to say so much.

571
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:13,720
Her mother is definitely an accomplice, no doubt about it.

572
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:15,520
We can go back and close the case.

573
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:16,880
It's just that,

574
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,040
these days,

575
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:20,480
there are all kinds of ways to kill.

576
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,300
We've checked carefully.

577
00:32:25,320 --> 00:32:26,880
When Fan Le and Niu Dali died,

578
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:28,480
he was working in the silk workshop.

579
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,000
So he didn't have time to commit the crime.

580
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:30,800
Constable Su.

581
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,860
Where is Zhao Xuanli's house?

582
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:33,760
Here.

583
00:32:58,480 --> 00:32:59,280
Constable Su.

584
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:02,480
Did Zhao Xuanli's father also fall here back then?

585
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,480
Right here.

586
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:08,240
I know the suspect's method.

587
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:10,840
Call Zhao Xuanli and her mother back.

588
00:33:11,320 --> 00:33:13,840
I want to recreate the crime for them.

